---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<main>

		<!-- ══ SECTION 1: Intro Split ══ -->
		<section class="intro" data-theme="classic-cream">
			<div class="intro__image reveal-fade">
				<img
					src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1300402/pexels-photo-1300402.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=900"
					alt="Photographer portrait"
					width="900" height="600"
					loading="eager" decoding="async"
				/>
			</div>
			<div class="intro__content">
				<div class="intro__text-wrap">
					<h1 class="intro__heading">Hi, I'm [Photographer Name]</h1>{/* TODO:NICHE */}
					<p class="intro__sub reveal reveal-delay-1">A photographer based in [City], here to help you document your story in a way that feels natural and stress-free.</p>{/* TODO:NICHE */}
					<p class="intro__body reveal reveal-delay-2">I've spent the last decade photographing the moments that matter most — the quiet ones, the joyful ones, the ones you don't even notice are happening until the camera catches them. My approach is unhurried and entirely led by you.</p>{/* TODO:NICHE */}
					<p class="intro__body reveal reveal-delay-3">What started as a personal project became a calling. I believe every person, every family, every bond deserves to be documented beautifully — not in a stiff, posed way, but in a way that is completely, unmistakably them.</p>{/* TODO:NICHE */}
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ══ SECTION 2: What to Expect ══ -->
		<section class="expect" data-theme="warm-studio">
			<hr />
			<div class="expect__inner">
				<div class="expect__label-col" aria-hidden="true">
					<span class="expect__label">What to Expect</span>
				</div>
				<div class="expect__cols">
					<div class="expect__col reveal reveal-delay-1">
						<div class="expect__img-wrap">
							<img
								src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/2253275/pexels-photo-2253275.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600&h=600&fit=crop"
								alt="Subject-led session in golden afternoon light"
								width="600" height="600"
								loading="lazy" decoding="async"
							/>
						</div>
						<p class="expect__col-label">Subject-Led Sessions</p>{/* TODO:NICHE */}
						<p class="expect__col-body">Every session moves at your pace. There are no forced poses or rigid shot lists — just space for you to be yourself while I follow the light and the moments as they unfold.</p>{/* TODO:NICHE */}
					</div>
					<div class="expect__col reveal reveal-delay-2">
						<div class="expect__img-wrap">
							<img
								src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/825949/pexels-photo-825949.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600&h=600&fit=crop"
								alt="Calm and supportive direction during a session"
								width="600" height="600"
								loading="lazy" decoding="async"
							/>
						</div>
						<p class="expect__col-label">Calm Supportive Direction</p>{/* TODO:NICHE */}
						<p class="expect__col-body">I'll gently guide you through the session so you never feel unsure of what to do. Most people tell me they forget the camera is there — that's exactly the point.</p>{/* TODO:NICHE */}
					</div>
					<div class="expect__col reveal reveal-delay-3">
						<div class="expect__img-wrap">
							<img
								src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1108099/pexels-photo-1108099.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600&h=600&fit=crop"
								alt="A genuine moment of connection"
								width="600" height="600"
								loading="lazy" decoding="async"
							/>
						</div>
						<p class="expect__col-label">Connection</p>{/* TODO:NICHE */}
						<p class="expect__col-body">The best photographs come from real connection. I invest time before every session getting to know you so that what we create together feels personal, not generic.</p>{/* TODO:NICHE */}
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ══ SECTION 3: Personal Split ══ -->
		<section class="personal" data-theme="classic-cream">
			<div class="personal__text reveal reveal-delay-1">
				<p class="personal__body"><em>Photography found me at a time when I needed it most. A camera in hand became a reason to look closely at the world — to slow down, notice the small things, and find beauty in the ordinary.</em></p>{/* TODO:NICHE */}
				<p class="personal__body"><em>That sense of attention is something I bring to every session. I'm not here to manufacture a perfect image. I'm here to find the one that's already there, waiting.</em></p>{/* TODO:NICHE */}
			</div>
			<div class="personal__image">
				<img
					src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1805164/pexels-photo-1805164.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=900"
					alt="Candid moment captured during a photography session"
					width="900" height="600"
					loading="lazy" decoding="async"
				/>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ══ SECTION 4: Pull Quote ══ -->
		<section class="pullquote" data-theme="classic-cream">
			<hr />
			<div class="pullquote__inner">
				<blockquote class="pullquote__text reveal reveal-delay-1">
					&ldquo;I believe photographs should feel honest, timeless, and personal.&rdquo;
				</blockquote>
				<a href="/contact" class="pullquote__link reveal reveal-delay-2">Work with me &rarr;</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ══ SECTION 5: Let's Do This CTA ══ -->
		<section class="cta" data-theme="warm-studio">
			<hr />
			<div class="cta__inner">
				<div class="cta__images">
					<div class="cta__img-back">
						<img
							src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3726314/pexels-photo-3726314.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600&h=750&fit=crop"
							alt="Photography session moment"
							width="600" height="750"
							loading="lazy" decoding="async"
						/>
					</div>
					<div class="cta__img-front">
						<img
							src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1254140/pexels-photo-1254140.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=500&h=640&fit=crop"
							alt="Another moment from a photography session"
							width="500" height="640"
							loading="lazy" decoding="async"
						/>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="cta__content">
					<h2 class="cta__heading reveal reveal-delay-1">Let's Do This!</h2>{/* TODO:NICHE */}
					<p class="cta__body reveal reveal-delay-2">If you're ready to have photographs that actually look and feel like you, I'd love to hear from you. Get in touch and let's start planning something special.</p>{/* TODO:NICHE */}
					<a href="/contact" class="cta__btn reveal reveal-delay-3">Get In Touch</a>
					<p class="cta__caption">Serving [City] and surrounding areas.</p>{/* TODO:NICHE */}
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	/* ══ SECTION 1: Intro ══ */
	.intro {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 400px 1fr;
		min-height: 90vh;
		max-width: 1100px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}

	.intro__image {
		overflow: hidden;
		height: 100%;
		padding-left: 3rem;
	}

	.intro__image img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
		object-position: center top;
		display: block;
	}

	.intro__content {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 6rem 5rem 6rem 6rem;
		border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
	}

	.intro__text-wrap {
		max-width: 560px;
	}

	.intro__heading {
		font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
		color: var(--text);
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
		line-height: 1.12;
	}

	.intro__sub {
		font-family: var(--font-sans);
		font-style: normal;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.14em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: var(--accent);
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}

	.intro__body {
		font-style: normal;
		font-size: 1.0625rem;
		line-height: 1.82;
		color: var(--muted);
		margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
	}

	/* ══ SECTION 2: What to Expect ══ */
	.expect {
		padding: 0 0 6rem;
	}

	.expect__inner {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr;
		padding: 0 3rem;
		max-width: 1100px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.expect__label-col {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.expect__label {
		font-family: var(--font-serif);
		font-style: italic;
		font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 2.25rem);
		letter-spacing: 0.12em;
		color: var(--border);
		writing-mode: vertical-rl;
		transform: rotate(180deg);
		white-space: nowrap;
		user-select: none;
	}

	.expect__cols {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 2.5rem;
		padding-top: 5rem;
	}

	.expect__img-wrap {
		overflow: hidden;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.expect__img-wrap img {
		width: 100%;
		aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
		object-fit: cover;
		display: block;
		transition: transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
	}

	.expect__img-wrap:hover img {
		transform: scale(1.04);
	}

	.expect__col-label {
		font-family: var(--font-sans);
		font-style: normal;
		font-size: 0.7rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.2em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: var(--text);
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.expect__col-body {
		font-size: 0.9375rem;
		line-height: 1.78;
		color: var(--muted);
	}

	/* ══ SECTION 3: Personal Split ══ */
	.personal {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		min-height: 70vh;
	}

	.personal__text {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 6rem 5rem;
		text-align: center;
		border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
	}

	.personal__body {
		font-family: var(--font-serif);
		font-style: italic;
		font-size: clamp(1.0625rem, 1.75vw, 1.25rem);
		line-height: 1.82;
		color: var(--text);
		max-width: 420px;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.personal__body:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.personal__body em {
		font-style: normal;
	}

	.personal__image {
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.personal__image img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
		object-position: center;
		display: block;
	}

	/* ══ SECTION 4: Pull Quote ══ */
	.pullquote {
		padding: 0 0 6rem;
	}

	.pullquote__inner {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 5rem 3rem 0;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.pullquote__text {
		font-family: var(--font-serif);
		font-style: italic;
		font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
		line-height: 1.45;
		color: var(--text);
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}

	.pullquote__link {
		font-style: italic;
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: var(--accent);
		text-decoration: none;
		letter-spacing: 0.01em;
		display: block;
		text-align: right;
		transition: opacity 0.2s, letter-spacing 0.25s;
	}

	.pullquote__link:hover {
		opacity: 1;
		letter-spacing: 0.04em;
	}

	/* ══ SECTION 5: CTA ══ */
	.cta {
		padding: 0 0 7rem;
	}

	.cta__inner {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 5rem;
		max-width: 1100px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 6rem 3rem 0;
	}

	/* Overlapping stacked images */
	.cta__images {
		position: relative;
		height: 520px;
	}

	.cta__img-back {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 75%;
		overflow: hidden;
		box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
	}

	.cta__img-back img {
		width: 100%;
		display: block;
		height: 420px;
		object-fit: cover;
	}

	.cta__img-front {
		position: absolute;
		bottom: 0;
		right: 0;
		width: 62%;
		overflow: hidden;
		box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.14);
	}

	.cta__img-front img {
		width: 100%;
		display: block;
		height: 340px;
		object-fit: cover;
	}

	.cta__heading {
		font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 4vw, 3.75rem);
		color: var(--text);
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
	}

	.cta__body {
		font-style: italic;
		font-size: 1.0625rem;
		line-height: 1.82;
		color: var(--text);
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		max-width: 420px;
	}

	.cta__btn {
		display: inline-block;
		font-family: var(--font-sans);
		font-style: normal;
		font-size: 0.7rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.2em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: var(--text);
		text-decoration: none;
		border: 1px solid var(--text);
		padding: 0.7rem 1.75rem;
		transition: background 0.25s, color 0.25s, transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.25s;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.cta__btn:hover {
		background: var(--text);
		color: var(--bg);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(26, 39, 68, 0.18);
	}

	.cta__caption {
		font-family: var(--font-sans);
		font-size: 0.8125rem;
		color: var(--muted);
		letter-spacing: 0.04em;
	}

	/* ══ Responsive ══ */
	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.intro {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.intro__image {
			padding-left: 1.5rem;
		}

		.intro__image img {
			height: 75vw;
			min-height: 320px;
		}

		.intro__content {
			padding: 4rem 2rem;
			border-left: none;
			border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
		}

		.intro__text-wrap {
			max-width: none;
		}

		.expect__inner {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			padding: 0 1.5rem;
		}

		.expect__label-col {
			display: none;
		}

		.expect__cols {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			padding-top: 3rem;
		}

		.personal {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.personal__text {
			padding: 4rem 2rem;
			border-right: none;
			border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
		}

		.personal__image img {
			height: 60vw;
			min-height: 300px;
		}

		.pullquote__inner {
			padding: 4rem 1.5rem 0;
		}

		.cta__inner {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 3rem;
			padding: 4rem 1.5rem 0;
		}

		.cta__images {
			height: 380px;
		}

		.cta__img-back img {
			height: 300px;
		}

		.cta__img-front img {
			height: 240px;
		}
	}
</style>
